            Git Repository: <a class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" href="https://github.com/sagedemage/DiscussionBoard"> DiscussionBoard </a></p>
		<ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
			<li> Implemented CI/CD with GitHub workflows to automate unit testing of the app </li>
			<li> Built user authentication so that users can register, login, and logout their account </li>
			<li> Designed password validation for user registration to check if the password is strong </li>
		</ul>

		<p class="font-bold text-2xl border-b-2 border-gray-300 mb-2 mt-2 pb-2"> Technical Skills </p>
		<p class="border-b border-gray-300 pb-2 mb-2"> <b>Languages</b>:
			JavaScript/TypeScript, Python, Go, HTML/CSS, Rust, Bash, Java, and PHP
		</p>
		<p class="border-b border-gray-300 pb-2 mb-2"> <b>Frameworks</b>: 
			Angular, Django, Flask, Gin, Next.js, Astro, and Bootstrap </p>
		<p class="border-b border-gray-300 pb-2 mb-2"> <b>Databases</b>: MySQL, MS SQL, and SQLite </p>
		<p class="border-b border-gray-300 pb-2 mb-2"> <b>Libraries</b>: React, Pandas, and jQuery </p>
